{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/post/faster-airpods-connect/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Gary Tietjen","author":"Gary Tietjen","homepage":"https://www.garyt.me"}},"post":{"id":"56e8947f-d5bf-5fe7-8cb6-eb79eb800e03","html":"<p>Switching between devices is already pretty seamless with AirPods. Once they’ve been paired to one of your Apple products, they will instantly be accessible on any other Apple products you own. The one thing I’ve found annoying is that while it connects pretty quickly on iOS, it’s a bit slower on macOS and there’s no keyboard shortcut. Let’s fix that.</p>\n<h2>Install Homebrew</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://brew.sh/\">Homebrew</a> is a package manager for macOS. You can install it with this command:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"hljs-js\"><code class=\"hljs-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>bin<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>bash <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>c <span class=\"token string\">\"$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install.sh)\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Install BluetoothConnector</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/lapfelix/BluetoothConnector\">BluetoothConnector</a> is a macOS CLI to connect/disconnect a Bluetooth device. It’s not limited to AirPods. It will make connecting any bluetooth devices to your Mac easier. Once Homebrew is installed you can install BluetoothConnector with this command:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"hljs-js\"><code class=\"hljs-js\">brew install bluetoothconnector</code></pre></div>\n<p>Once it’s installed, run this command to get a list of bluetooth devices and their corresponding MAC address.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"hljs-js\"><code class=\"hljs-js\">bluetoothconnector</code></pre></div>\n<p>Copy the MAC address next to your AirPods and open Automator. Select “Quick Action” as your document type.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 997px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.22266800401204%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/de6901c813144b4c3455615963abc004/1e0be/automator2.webp 250w,\n/static/de6901c813144b4c3455615963abc004/b0a15/automator2.webp 500w,\n/static/de6901c813144b4c3455615963abc004/c5bb7/automator2.webp 997w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 997px) 100vw, 997px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/de6901c813144b4c3455615963abc004/63868/automator2.png 250w,\n/static/de6901c813144b4c3455615963abc004/0b533/automator2.png 500w,\n/static/de6901c813144b4c3455615963abc004/ec3e2/automator2.png 997w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 997px) 100vw, 997px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/de6901c813144b4c3455615963abc004/ec3e2/automator2.png\"\n          alt=\"automator\"\n          title=\"automator\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span><a href=\"\"></a></p>\n<p>Change the “Workflow receives current” dropdown to “no input”.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 992px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.29435483870968%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/675179185a34cf852363b318d003f776/1e0be/automator4.webp 250w,\n/static/675179185a34cf852363b318d003f776/b0a15/automator4.webp 500w,\n/static/675179185a34cf852363b318d003f776/9012d/automator4.webp 992w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 992px) 100vw, 992px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/675179185a34cf852363b318d003f776/63868/automator4.png 250w,\n/static/675179185a34cf852363b318d003f776/0b533/automator4.png 500w,\n/static/675179185a34cf852363b318d003f776/91f10/automator4.png 992w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 992px) 100vw, 992px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/675179185a34cf852363b318d003f776/91f10/automator4.png\"\n          alt=\"automator\"\n          title=\"automator\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span><a href=\"\"></a></p>\n<p>Drag “Run Shell Script” from the left sidebar into your workflow. And add this command to the text area: </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"hljs-js\"><code class=\"hljs-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>usr<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>local<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>bin<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>BluetoothConnector <span class=\"token constant\">YOUR</span> <span class=\"token constant\">AIRPODS</span> <span class=\"token constant\">MAC</span> <span class=\"token constant\">ADDRESS</span> <span class=\"token operator\">--</span>notify</code></pre></div>\n<p>Replace YOUR AIRPODS MAC ADDRESS with the MAC address you copied earlier. It should look something like this:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 995px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.37185929648241%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/6bca0faeb024764c2512cff5be22984d/1e0be/automator3.webp 250w,\n/static/6bca0faeb024764c2512cff5be22984d/b0a15/automator3.webp 500w,\n/static/6bca0faeb024764c2512cff5be22984d/157c9/automator3.webp 995w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 995px) 100vw, 995px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/6bca0faeb024764c2512cff5be22984d/63868/automator3.png 250w,\n/static/6bca0faeb024764c2512cff5be22984d/0b533/automator3.png 500w,\n/static/6bca0faeb024764c2512cff5be22984d/4cdf7/automator3.png 995w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 995px) 100vw, 995px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/6bca0faeb024764c2512cff5be22984d/4cdf7/automator3.png\"\n          alt=\"automator\"\n          title=\"automator\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span><a href=\"\"></a></p>\n<p>Save the Automator Service as “Connect Airpods”. Open up System Preferences > Keyboard. Click on the Shortcuts tab. Select Services from the left sidebar and scroll down the right sidebar until you see the Connect AirPods Service. Click Add Shortcut and choose a keyboard shortcut. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 662px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 86.70694864048339%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/e41ee098d72aeb40ac4a368904d89c21/1e0be/keyboard.webp 250w,\n/static/e41ee098d72aeb40ac4a368904d89c21/b0a15/keyboard.webp 500w,\n/static/e41ee098d72aeb40ac4a368904d89c21/90cc3/keyboard.webp 662w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 662px) 100vw, 662px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/e41ee098d72aeb40ac4a368904d89c21/63868/keyboard.png 250w,\n/static/e41ee098d72aeb40ac4a368904d89c21/0b533/keyboard.png 500w,\n/static/e41ee098d72aeb40ac4a368904d89c21/be86f/keyboard.png 662w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 662px) 100vw, 662px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/e41ee098d72aeb40ac4a368904d89c21/be86f/keyboard.png\"\n          alt=\"keyboard settings\"\n          title=\"keyboard settings\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span><a href=\"\"></a></p>\n<p>Now you can quickly connect/disconnect your AirPods with a simple Keyboard shortcut. It’s much faster too!</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"A Faster Way to Connect AirPods to your Mac","path":"/post/faster-airpods-connect/","images":["./airpods-connect.png"],"heroimages":[{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":1.7797202797202798,"src":"/static/811e95e924e7517c13076fb1f0d54430/3c17d/airpods-connect.png","srcSet":"/static/811e95e924e7517c13076fb1f0d54430/e0491/airpods-connect.png 180w,\n/static/811e95e924e7517c13076fb1f0d54430/f4094/airpods-connect.png 360w,\n/static/811e95e924e7517c13076fb1f0d54430/3c17d/airpods-connect.png 720w,\n/static/811e95e924e7517c13076fb1f0d54430/64c42/airpods-connect.png 1018w","srcWebp":"/static/811e95e924e7517c13076fb1f0d54430/2aa8d/airpods-connect.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/811e95e924e7517c13076fb1f0d54430/1a890/airpods-connect.webp 180w,\n/static/811e95e924e7517c13076fb1f0d54430/b6bb8/airpods-connect.webp 360w,\n/static/811e95e924e7517c13076fb1f0d54430/2aa8d/airpods-connect.webp 720w,\n/static/811e95e924e7517c13076fb1f0d54430/d7d05/airpods-connect.webp 1018w","sizes":"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px"}},"publicURL":"/static/airpods-connect-811e95e924e7517c13076fb1f0d54430.png"}],"category":"","tags":[""],"date":"2018-01-09T00:00:00.000Z","components":null,"tweets":null,"summary":"Quickly connect your AirPods with a keyboard shortcut"}}},"pageContext":{}}}